node.text: that looks so soft and fluffy!

Together with @zatayayummy @shootandspoon , we decided to challenge ourselves with two tone Chiffon cake. 
Ta-Da...... Mine version ✌🏻 . 
Not the prettiest, but who cares 😂 . Just bake for fun. 
Am Glad to receive so many tips and advice from ZongHan and Cecil. Not my strength in baking cakes, but I love chiffon cakes 😋 . 
Definitely need to up skill it. 
We will be having our next bake soon.
Who wants to join us? .
.
For recipe, check it out at @zatayayummy IG :) .
